videos.headline: Michigan QB intercepted on first play of the season
videos.description: Michigan QB Wilton Speight is picked off by Hawaii's Damien Packer on the Wolverines' first play of the season.

videos.headline: Jim Harbaugh pumps up his quarterback.
videos.description: Michigan Head Coach Jim Harbaugh readies quarterback Wilton Speight prior to Michigan's game vs. Hawaii.

videos.description: Wilson Speight hits Grant Perry for a 12-yard touchdown to put Michigan ahead of Hawaii 7-0.

videos.headline: Jabrill Peppers shows absurd hops
videos.description: The play was called back due to a penalty, but Jabrill Peppers shows off his ridiculous hops by leaping over a defender while returning a punt.
